cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a new algorithm for continual learning in neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). The experiments conducted in the paper involve supervised learning benchmarks (cs.CV) and reinforcement learning environments (cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE, followed by cs.CV and cs.CL.
